A Vehicle Inspection Officer has been spotted clinging to a speeding truck along the Ughelli expressway in Delta State. The officer it was gathered had tried to stop the truck but the driver refused to stop. Angered by the act, the officer decided to cling on the truck. Watch video below: #VIO seen clinging to a speeding truck along the #Ughelli expressway in #DeltaState A post shared by  Instablog9ja (@instablog9ja) on Feb 25, 2020 at 7:52am PST Source